        ### Example usage ###
        
            import plinq
            linq = plinq.from_iterable([1, 2, 3, 4, 5]).where(lambda item, index: item % 2 == 0).select(lambda item, index: item ** 2)
            for item in linq:
                print(item)
        
        This will result in the following output:
        
            4
            16
        
